00:14:30.376 --> 00:14:32.718
SP: Deţinerea de arme nucleare.

00:14:32.718 --> 00:14:35.095
RNG: Apelul la religie pentru a justifica

00:14:35.095 --> 00:14:36.735
ce nu poate fi altfel motivat,

